<br>
“Uh huh,” she affirmed. “And in yours?” She asked. Clark ducked his head.<br>
<br>
“You were my dead sister,” he said in a half horrified, half ashamed voice. Lana, Pete, and Alison all burst out in laughter. Pete slapped him on the back.<br>
<br>
